title: Fill Your Head With Rock (1970) CBS Compilation Album From Vinyl
description:
This seminal Album from 1970 CBS Compilation Vinyl..signalled the end of 60s and the beginning of the 70s..This RARE item features artists who were virtually unknown at the time - artists such as: Black Widow, Flock, Janis Joplin, Taj Mahal, Al Kooper, Johnny Winter, Moondog, Pacific Gas & Electric, Chicago, Blood Sweat and Tears, Tom Rush, Trees, Byrds to name but a few.

For more info about this album check out these sites and see the album artwork..
